You revoke your right to pursue litigation against the health organization in the event of a data breach. Issues, controversies, and concerns will be remediated following legal procedures.

Robust Software Solutions hold the right to store your requested personal data in the event of product unavailability. The Health Application is licensed, not sold and is protected by domestic and international copyright intellectual property laws. You may identify and correct software errors prior to purchasing the license. The health application will adhere to data protection guidelines established by the GDPR Compliancy (EU), and Data Protection Act (UK).
